                <div type="section" xml:id="recognition">
                    <head>Recognition</head>
                    <div type="timeline">
                        <head>British Recognition of U.S. Independence, <date when="1783"
                                >1783</date>.</head>
                        <p>The United Kingdom officially recognized American independence by signing
                            the <ref target="/milestones/1776-1783/treaty">Treaty of Paris of
                                1783</ref>. David Hartley, a Member of Parliament representing
                            British King George III, signed the treaty along with the American
                            delegation of <ref target="/departmenthistory/people/adams-john">John
                                Adams</ref>, <ref
                                target="/departmenthistory/people/franklin-benjamin">Benjamin
                                Franklin</ref>, and <ref target="/departmenthistory/people/jay-john"
                                >John Jay </ref>on September 3, 1783.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
